msgid ":guilabel:`Provider`: select :guilabel:`OnSIP`."
msgstr ":guilabel:`Provider`: виберіть :guilabel:`OnSIP`."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/phone/onsip.rst:68
msgid ":guilabel:`Username`: the user's :guilabel:`OnSIP username`."
msgstr ":guilabel:`Username`: :guilabel:`OnSIP username` користувача."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/phone/onsip.rst:69
msgid ":guilabel:`OnSIP Auth Username`: the user's :guilabel:`Auth Username`."
msgstr ":guilabel:`OnSIP Auth Username`: :guilabel:`Auth Username` користувача."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/phone/onsip.rst:70
msgid ":guilabel:`Secret`: the user's :guilabel:`SIP Password`."
msgstr ":guilabel:`Secret`: :guilabel:`SIP Password` користувача."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/phone/onsip.rst:72
msgid ""
"Once the OnSIP credentials have been saved, the user can make calls with "
"Odoo **Phone** by clicking the :icon:`oi-voip` :guilabel:`(Phone)` icon in "
"the top-right corner of Odoo."
msgstr ""
"Після збереження облікових даних OnSIP користувач може здійснювати дзвінки "
"за допомогою Odoo **Phone**, натиснувши значок :icon:`oi-voip` :guilabel:`"
"(Phone)` у верхньому правому куті Odoo."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/phone/onsip.rst:76
msgid ""
"For additional setup and troubleshooting steps, see `OnSIP's knowledge base "
